#

Cheesy Mashed Potato Casserole

60 min
$10
320 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 6

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

Vegetarian

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main DishSide Dish

Tags:

CasseroleComfort FoodCheesyPotatoes

Description

A creamy, cheesy delight that turns simple mashed potatoes into a comforting casserole.

Ingredients

  • mashed potatoes: 4 cups
  • cream cheese: 8 oz
  • sour cream: 1 cup
  • shredded cheddar cheese: 2 cups
  • green onions: 1/4 cup
  • garlic powder: 1 tsp
  • salt: 1 tsp
  • black pepper: 1/2 tsp
  • butter: 2 tbsp
